Bibliographic References: Cat. (1985), p. 71 (ill.); ex London Market, Sotheby, Sale Cat. 5 July 1982, no. 337, ill. on p. 120; ex Charles Ede, GPSIVl, 1978, no. 29; VIII, 1982, no. 25 (ill.); ex Zurich Market, Arete.
Imagery Description: (a) Draped woman by stele, holding phiale and wreath, (b) nude youth with phiale moving to right and looking back left.
Additional Notes: The picture on (a) is framed by reserved bands, with triangles at the top; on (b) by scrolls with dropNon Sepcifiedleaf.
